    <item>
      <title>日本领导人候选人高市呼吁日本央行继续宽松政策</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-09-14/japan-leadership-hopeful-takaichi-calls-for-boj-to-keep-easing</link>
      <description><![CDATA[日本下任首相的一位主要候选人表示，日本央行放弃超宽松政策为时过早，因为即将参加本月执政党选举的九名议员在周六的新闻发布会上发生了争论。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-09-14/japan-leadership-hopeful-takaichi-calls-for-boj-to-keep-easing</guid>
      <pubDate>Sat, 14 Sep 2024 10:11:44 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>德国连续两周遭遇坏消息</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-09-14/germany-struggles-with-two-terrible-weeks-of-bad-news</link>
      <description><![CDATA[德国挺过了新冠疫情，并在俄罗斯切断天然气供应后避免了灾难性的工业停工。尽管如此，这仍未完全消除人们对未来可能出现经济困境的担忧。过去两周的情况提供了戏剧性的证据，证明这些担忧是有道理的。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-09-14/germany-struggles-with-two-terrible-weeks-of-bad-news</guid>
      <pubDate>Sat, 14 Sep 2024 06:59:43 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
